s/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"7/10<br />\n如有更多hr金句，會更高分<br />\n例：俾個理由我點解要請你<br />\n例2 ： 你計劃十年後會做到咩level"},{"pid":"c9b281dcc5d549b4594b584b41206775f8382fe1","tid":883704,"uid":208159,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce62627a6112b3435f88cdcc8a734d9ecd8f85d5","tid":883704,"uid":117472,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26293702&amp;extra=&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D26293702%26extra%3D%26page%3D1&d=HetuhokjshoFeYmKQ5or8V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=08c2b7b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=26293702&amp;extra=&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n此post已完"},{"pid":"5c15576e8503632c2244dcac88d8acc5bf9685c3","tid":883704,"uid":77092,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bd956d80d3e4479484f21ba5bd4ad9d904744e1","tid":883704,"uid":206471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"唔好笑嗰下&quot;宅洗&quot;啊 阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41f15e27d20d9687a791f0e622df045a23a9b60","tid":883704,"uid":21249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"留名聽日上晴報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b17cfdc2a0f3ae32d43202ed9669c45e7f954b","tid":883704,"uid":22738,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"sorry呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係果位應徵者,而家冇人請好慘<img src=\"/as